Hi,

There may be more elegant ways but here is one solution.

sample.name <- c("ABC_study_provider", "XYZ_study_provider")
lapply(sample.name,
    function(xx) {
        filename <- paste0(xx, ".rda")
        ## make the GAlignmentPairs
        ## ...
        xx <- GAlignmentPairs()
        save(xx, file=filename)
    })

Val


